OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, River groups have called for a review  
OL,6, of how water pollution incidents are   
OL,7, investigated in Wales.                 
OL,9,FThousands of small-scale spills are not
OL,10,Feven being looked into, they said,     
OL,11,Fadding up to a "massive issue".        
OL,13,FIt follows criticism of a leaked       
OL,14,Fdocument suggesting staff at England's 
OL,15,FEnvironment Agency (EA) should ignore  
OL,16,Flow-impact pollution events.           
OL,18,FNatural Resources Wales (NRW) said     
OL,19,Fincident management was a crucial part 
OL,20,Fof its work.                           
